                <li>
                  <p>
                  What relationship do you see among the vectors <m>\overrightarrow{AB}</m>, <m>\overrightarrow{BC}</m>, and <m>\overrightarrow{AC}</m>? Explain why this relationship should hold.
                  </p>
                </li>
