          <p>
            A <em>unit vector</em> is a vector whose magnitude is 1. Of the vectors <m>\textbf{i}</m>, <m>\textbf{j}</m>, and <m>\textbf{i} + \textbf{            j}</m>, which are unit vectors?
          </p>
        </li>

